results.latest_major_action: Placed on Senate Legislative Calendar under General Orders. Calendar No. 124.
results.summary: Alex Diekmann Peak Designation Act of 2017 This bill designates as the Alex Diekmann Peak the 9,765-foot peak located 2.2 miles west-northwest of Finger Mountain on the western boundary of the Lee Metcalf Wilderness in Montana.
results.summary_short: Alex Diekmann Peak Designation Act of 2017 This bill designates as the Alex Diekmann Peak the 9,765-foot peak located 2.2 miles west-northwest of Finger Mountain on the western boundary of the Lee Metcalf Wilderness in Montana.
